# ── Contact Form Backend ──

# ── Option A: Formspree (recommended for GH Pages / static export) ──
# Free tier: 50 submissions/month, email notifications, spam protection.
# 1. Sign up at https://formspree.io
# 2. Create a new form → copy the form ID from your form URL
# 3. Set the ID below (e.g. xpwqvoal from https://formspree.io/f/xpwqvoal)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_FORMSPREE_ID=your_form_id_here

# ── Option B: OCI Object Storage (for self-hosted / server-side deploys) ──
# The API route at app/api/contact/route.ts handles submissions server-side.
# OCI CLI auth comes from ~/.oci/config — no extra env vars needed.
# CONTACT_API_TOKEN=your_token_for_GET_endpoint

# ── GitHub Pages Deployment ──
# 1. Set NEXT_PUBLIC_FORMSPREE_ID (see above)
# 2. Run: npm run deploy:gh-pages
#    This removes app/api (static export doesn't support API routes),
#    builds with basePath="/portfolio", deploys to gh-pages branch.
# 3. In GitHub repo Settings → Pages → Source: gh-pages branch
# 4. Site will be at: https://callmeamps.github.io/portfolio/